726753f-b.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - Goldsmith Street
726753f-b.text:
Grand Avenue, south side betwee Goldsmith and Van Loon
Streets, showing two views of the Goldsmith house. Eliza
F. Leverich, a daughter of Col. Edward Leverich who died in
1833, married the Rev. John Goldsmith. Mrs. Goldsmith was the
owner in 1873 and J.H. Prall in 1891.
1922
View 21June 1925.
Eugene . Armbruster Collection
